col30: I sometimes feel resentful when I don't get my way.
col31: On a few occasions, I have given up doing something because I thought too little of my ability.
col32: There have been times when I felt like rebelling against people in authority even though I knew they were right.
col33: No matter who I'm talking to, I'm always a good listener.
col34: I can remember "playing sick" to get out of something.
col35: There have been occasions when I took advantage of someone.
col36: I'm always willing to admit it when I make a mistake.
col37: I sometimes try to get even rather than forgive and forget.
col38: I am always courteous, even to people who are disagreeable.
col39: I have never been irked when people expressed ideas very different from my own.
col40: There have been times when I was quite jealous of the good fortune of others.
col41: I am sometimes irritated by people who ask favors of me.
col42: I have never deliberately said something that hurt someone's feelings.
